Personal Blackbox tracks how you are driving, how healthy you car is, and in case of accidents, which other cars are nearby.

Even the best drivers can improve their driving, and in the unfortunate case of an accident, knowing who else was nearby can be the difference between a clean driving record you, 

Personal Blackbox records everything about your car and your surroundings. Know your teenagers are driving safely, and if any incidents should occur, from fender-benders to hit-and-runs, know what happened to your car, and ID the cell phones and bluetooth radios nearby to find witnesses and perpetrators. 